title: Converse Rubber Tracks: Minor Soul records "That's Just Love"
description:
Recorded at Converse Rubber Tracks, Minor Soul's single "That's Just Love" is this week's "Track of the Week". The band wasted no time exploring the state-of-the-art equipment that the studio had to offer, all supplied by Guitar Center and dove right into recording the original single.
For more on Converse Rubber Tracks: 
http://www.converse.com/rubbertracks
